Package: martini
Type: Package
Title: BMDI MLAI pipeline - Prepare Module
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Ahrens", "Maike", email = "maike.ahrens@chrestos.de", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Voss", "Sebastian", email = "sebastian.voss@chrestos.de", role = c("aut")))
Description: Prepare module of the BMDI MLAI pipeline. It contains functions to conveniently
  transform a set of ADaM data sets (adsl, bds and occds) into a data object that can be used
  for machine learning, e.g. using the BMDI MLAI pipeline.
